{"title":"细雪","authors":["周晓萍"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":3,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"细雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周晓萍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天空有点儿蓝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"充满了内心一样洁白的雨点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我绝对真挚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且冷中有热"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道你没有感受到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我铺天盖地的柔情？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但在风口上，我却变得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像玻璃钢一样坚强"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说不清是大地融化了我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是我融化了大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我知道，这些日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天藏在一件红毛衣里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼之欲出——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一朵雪花在路旁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗤嗤地响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗宁静的心呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"痛苦而美好地裂开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我恨自己太轻柔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恨在漫天飞雪中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口不能言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如水年华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎能在地老天荒中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年复一年地消溶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哎，快点抬起头来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天就在前方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"展现得美丽而及时"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":11,"page_end":11}